t offenbart. Die koreanische Autorin schärft damit das Bewusstsein für die kulturellen Besonderheiten dieses Landes und gibt hilfreiche Tipps, die die konfliktfreie Zusammenarbeit im Arbeitsalltag erleichtern.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 0aBusiness etiquettezKorea (South) 0aInternational business enterpriseszKorea (South) 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAsian Studies Backlist (2000-2014) eBook Packagez978311064977208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Social Sciences 2000 - 2014z9783110638080oZDB-23-GSS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Politik- und Sozialwissenschaften 2013z9783110342741oZDB-23-OPS0 cprintz978348674863540uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978348685810540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486858105423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486858105/original  a978-3-11-064977-2  Asian Studies Backlist (2000-2014) eBook Packagec2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GSSc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OPSb2013